nnsec.net
Class Net

java.lang.Object
  nnsec.net.Net
All Implemented Interfaces:
NetIFace
public class Net
extends java.lang.Object
implements NetIFace

Net class represents main implementation of NetIFace. Instances of this class are neural networks that server exports to the clients and clients want to use.
